snippet.title: Astral Ascent - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Live on Kickstarter, get your physical editions - https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/hibernian-workshop/astral-ascent
Wishlist on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1280930/Astral_Ascent/
Join our Discord - https://discord.com/invite/hibernian-workshop
Follow us on Twitter - https://twitter.com/HibernianWS

Astral Ascent is a 2D platformer rogue-lite set in a modern fantasy world. As one (or two in local co-op) of 4 Heroes with colorful personalities, you must escape from the Garden, an astral prison guarded by 12 powerful and vicious bosses—the Zodiacs!
